member.summary: Specify whether CrashReporter.NET should send anonymous crash report to Doctor Dump that doesn't contain private information. Only about 1/10 of users press "Send" button on crash reporting dialogs. And even less if there are required fields to fill. Without sending anonymous reports most of the problems are hidden from the developer.
